FBIS4-10854 "drlat075_m_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-075 Daily Report 18 Apr 1994 Brazil Colombia Expels 200 Brazilian Gold Miners Colombia Expels 200 Brazilian Gold Miners PY1904011394 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network in Portuguese 2200 GMT 18 Apr 94 PY1904011394 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network Portuguese BFN [Text] The Colombian Government last weekend expelled 200 Brazilian gold miners who were clandestinely working in Colombia. This was reported today by regional Federal Police Superintendent Mauro Esposito. He said the gold miners were sent to Tabatinga and are now on their way to Manaus.
